cerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo eyes will never touch the Hellfire: an eye weeping from the fear of Allah, and an eye standing guard in the way of Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1639 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21031,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/13\/fatwa-hikmah-ibn-abbas\/","url_meta":{"origin":14170,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Fatwa: Wisdom in issuing legal verdicts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn 'Ubaydah reported: A man came to Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, and he said, \u201cIs there repentance for one who kills a believer?\u201d Ibn Abbas said, \u201cNo, there is nothing but Hellfire.\u201d After the man left, those sitting nearby said to him, \u201cWhat is this?\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28831,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/08\/tafsir-quran-ignorance\/","url_meta":{"origin":14170,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tafsir: Warning not to interpret Quran without knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever speaks on the Quran without knowledge, let him take his sea